Show patient_id, first_name, last_name from patients whos diagnosis is 'Dementia'.

Primary diagnosis is stored in the admissions table.

select p.patient_id, p.first_name, p.last_name from patients p left join admissions a on p.patient_id = a.patient_id where a.diagnosis = 'Dementia';

